{"type": "article", "id": 39751, "title": "Prada 要重点发展电商，以及，LV 最新的“大师”联名款发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-04-13T03:11:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 1038, "name": "Flyknit"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 39345, "name": "2017 上海时装周"}, {"id": 39464, "name": "Damir Doma"}, {"id": 39465, "name": "大阪环球影城"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 121, "name": "Jeff Koons"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170413104104YrTpolIP4aKfuyez.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/business/earnings/puma-increases-full-year-guidance-shoes-337146/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>第一季度增长强劲，PUMA 发布 2017 全年计划</b></a> | PUMA 预计，2017 年将保持较低的两位数增长。全年盈利将下降至 1.85 亿至 2 亿欧元之间。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/prada-focus-digital-business-10866157/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Prada 2016 财年利润大跌，将重点做电商</strong></a> | 截止 1 月 31 日，Prada 的 2016 财年录得 2.783 亿欧元，比起去年的 3.309 亿欧元下降了 15.9%。另外，Prada 打算重点发展电商，找了新的团队来做数字化，翻新电商网站，2017 年品牌所有的产品都会放在网上售卖。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/04/11/jeff-koons-louis-vuitton-masters/#slide-3\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 最新的一个重磅联名，找来了波普艺术大师 Jeff Koons</a>。该联名系列名为 masters，Jeff 把经典画作移植到手提袋款上，推出了包括手提包、双肩包、丝巾在内的多款单品。另外， Jeff Koons 还将 Louis Vuitton 的 Monogram 图案加入自己名字缩写，这是 LV 首次允许更改 Monogram 的图案设计。这个系列是双方的首次合作，将于 4 月 28 日正式登场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104821VU1m0F5zphc6tNJQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104822hXBSsO0HT6vmrI51.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105113LS9yv26ruF8OPaeH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131048225KNRYQt7MxmI0h2S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104822AizhSGH4RE6Ko9XW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104821BmnTIZNusgKc8Mtx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104821Kx97g4LO1RtCd0UX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/visvim-geta-sandal-2017-spring-summer\" rel=\"nofollow\">visvim 2017 春夏系列带来全新的木屐设计</a>。该系列共包括红、黑、蓝三色复古方巾制成的三款木屐，均选用了天然泡桐木制作，在后跟处还有特别的图案设计。这个木屐系列现已于旗舰店及<a href=\"http://www.visvim.tv/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a>发售，售价为 492 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102120o6YiQMwH5tznXcru.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667808\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102120tfjFA2iKz4HN06s1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131021202CkbOJU8Gm6doANx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666287\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102208XFZLqK0cVobiUQTB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665761\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131022083Ic0bUSOahjqTXBu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667800\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>大阪环球影城与《周刊少年 jump》合作的 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/universal-jump-summer-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Universal Jump Summer</a> 上，除了庆祝《One Piece》十周年以及《龙珠》主题外，还将加入《银魂》和《JoJo奇妙冒险》，展会期为今年 6 月 30 日至 10 月 1 日。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102226AL9pS1vBrEO2dV87.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/nike-free-run-motion-flyknit-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 发布全新跑鞋 Free Run Motion Flyknit 2017</a>。这款鞋采用了 Nike 的袜式造型，结合 Flyknit 针织材质，省去了系鞋带的麻烦。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102241mXn5erHvLpCbSABJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102242eagQSjZpr94ObwAI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上海时装周继续更新：</p><p><strong>Damir Doma</strong></p><p>生于克罗地亚，在德国长大的设计师 Damir Doma 先后师从知名设计师 Raf Simons 和 Dirk Schonberger ，并在 Raf Simons 的支持下于 2007 年发布同名服装品牌的第一个系列。</p><p>本次时装周上，Damir Doma 带来他的 2017 秋冬系列。本季以大地色系为主，采用不规则剪裁的呈现方式，将女性的柔软和潇洒完美地融合。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102908YJ1zwNa9Rg2xc0nW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102908IpQ1fndSGiVEPxWB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102909apmUMuEqCyP4xhd7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029096PqxXV8rKEFv9bBy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102909cReq9Ww3p2ikJCdt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102909Hk31Bg2wJimM8zTF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102912Mk8oTrSgeIlchJF6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102912tnyQ4bsXoelM7JfE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102914P4T3SIUdtyKwBlvE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102915cx5ItvPwH8Cpz9RB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102915qwZpFgckOJ9BUQ0W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102916JxoDHiwgEtQLNfX9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102916sJ6IY0Lpg1fE4jqe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102917op3uzEMfTR5wcX7G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029185A7mFlkhHY1nPeyM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102918gU6BDSN9brAdT1pi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102918U0YsG9pRKldinJMg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102919ND0mAqrlKRf3Boe5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>CINDY SOONG</strong></p><p>设计师宋楚仪毕业于 FIT 纽约时装学院，2012 年回国并成立独立服装工作室。</p><p>本季的产品也在保留品牌宽松廓形及暗黑风格中突破原本设计思维模式，从褶皱波浪细节剪裁入手以不同与往的设计点呈现独特的 CINDY SOONG 设计理念。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105440oQcvT3ntwdsxFLyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105442Xa3GERpvoqzcuTw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105442zixF5hBlTmkrUZty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131054435wIuS70jYNncU4td.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105443gBRq5PjYf1daVuT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105443TspjBYCz4vZbMINn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105444IZJwcYuLlnH4x9Xf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105446jWspmvBJLyPfcUiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105446fTtLVPZXnipJbYk9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105446PKjIRsq07cHtY6C9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105448z3cDQ1rKSYTa7EjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105448oA85w72kxu9LTgrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131054480T5Qnf8d3j6iqo71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105449yUCkLoJdMgbmKBrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131054482sLCh18ZiVmxRraE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105450nj7lVqZwzaRU2oJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105450dpszB3uUJOEFWkXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105451mi7z4TxCrgHk65y3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131054512459Q8P37LwEGNqv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413105452JyQmexhqZXDcI6pM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131054523W8jJpmSIM4bLBd7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b>MAY HSU</b><br></p><p>MAY HSU 秋冬玩弄的是组合搭配，没有特别强调面料的改良和创新，但在异素材的搭配和设计上，有别于一般的穿搭方式，比如说风衣面料本身强调保暖，设计上利用羽绒来增加体积感，夸张地利用其造型，兼具保暖时尚，比较硬挺帅气的面料也有利于和皮革的搭配，来形成视觉冲击。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102945U5Z7wcM4P9TuAehY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029451T5CbvWYhXctKEeD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029467DKbEVxHQaigNLtJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102946lCoAfWXOpdSvD2x9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102946FyUxHYtgua2SJv4c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029472YIaLH1sTEkVuDKy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102947Vfjprh0N3xLyFZs5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102948G9OFtI3wQARul7fN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029489aSxEhuDXjrb6ftK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131029488omlTNVry1HpDiB7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102949N8pXBkhqoJKVaFHT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102949yPDejY6kLqrpuKHW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102950uzowIQ0nkdKRE8C4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102950VXOzR4AjirvPYLIH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102951UsPXKozA54pI08RM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102951Y8NgO0lxRjHJ1VWX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413102951FDXkQzdbEpAqmRGe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>RAY CHU</strong></p><p>设计师朱柏谚于 2016 年在台北创办品牌 RAY CHU。本次时装周上发布 2017 秋冬系列新品。</p><p>该系列灵感来自生活于冬日潮湿的街头景象。面料质地上将透过不同层次诠释湿润地面反射于街景的光泽感和浸湿化开于柏油路面的斑驳。品牌紧扣实穿设计，线条简单利落，面料舒适且具张力，细节处理上选用各类五金装饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104521IAqXVkWBZpzri18l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131045213c9DBGjAHRfSd0Ox.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104521UyMTnNZjJiXwdL7g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104523mE9NPFuT0avtU8kf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104523xjcCm8Lvbs6ZVNDE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131045243nq8NYE9Oo0Mi45L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104524JzH27GyC5OXdZImS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>JOYRICH</strong></p><p>2008 年创立于洛杉矶的潮牌 JOYRICH，混合复古与前卫，代表新生代的时尚和文化。</p><p>2017 秋冬系列主题是洛杉矶“文艺复兴”，系列贯穿强烈的怀旧风格并融入讽刺的意味，廓形设计灵感来源于 90 年代。秋冬系列突出了 JOYRICH 品牌的独特性，品牌至今不断融合新兴的流行趋势及技术，但依旧保留其独特的个性和魅力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104131C7mcx0JFekXfZjtd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104132HphX3N0rFWOAnPfY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170413104133YxeR7cvjqOWosIDZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704131041330tI2TlnYsioqQS